name: Criers of the Pond
description: Receiving aid from the Mohoe in a time of great need, the Criers of the Pond were left with a deep seated gratitude towards the Mohoe. They're also known for their adept handling of dune surfers. Now having successfully domesticated compressor cats, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
